<div style="font-family: Montserrat, Arial, sans-serif; padding: 24px; background: #f5f7fa;">
  <div style="max-width: 1180px; margin: 0 auto;">

    <!-- Main shell -->
    <div style="position: relative; background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #d9e1e8; border-radius: 14px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(15,23,42,0.05); overflow: hidden;">

      <!-- Step number -->
      <div style="position: absolute; left: 16px; top: 16px; width: 32px; height: 32px; background: #0f9b94; color: #ffffff; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; z-index: 2;">
        2
      </div>

      <div style="margin-left: 52px;">

        <!-- Top row -->
        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 16px; padding: 18px 20px; background: #edf2f5; border-bottom: 1px solid #d9e1e8; flex-wrap: wrap;">
          <h2 style="margin: 0; font-size: 28px; line-height: 1.2; color: #14213d; font-weight: 700;">
            Lead Qualification
          </h2>
          <div style="white-space: nowrap; background: #c9f1e8; color: #117d74; border-radius: 999px; padding: 8px 14px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700;">
            Portal Status = Qualification in Progress
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Goal row -->
        <div style="padding: 16px 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid #d9e1e8; color: #5f6b7a; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.65;">
          <strong style="color: #24344d;">Goal:</strong>
          Confirm customer meets eligibility criteria before any pitch. Both teams use the same tool and process.
        </div>

        <!-- Body -->
        <div style="padding: 32px 20px 24px; text-align: center;">

          <!-- Dots -->
          <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 6px; margin-bottom: 18px;">
            <span style="width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; display: inline-block; background: #7a2ee6;"></span>
            <span style="width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; display: inline-block; background: #0f9b94;"></span>
          </div>

          <!-- Intro -->
          <p style="max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto 20px; font-size: 26px; line-height: 1.5; color: #24344d; font-weight: 500;">
            Both AMs use the same qualification tool and follow the same process.<br>
            The AM who logged the opportunity runs qualification.
          </p>

          <!-- Actions -->
          <ol style="max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto 28px; padding-left: 24px; text-align: left; color: #6a7685; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.9;">
            <li><span style="color: #6a7685;">Run the Qualification Tool to confirm eligibility</span></li>
            <li><span style="color: #6a7685;">Update Partner Portal to "Qualification in Progress"</span></li>
            <li><span style="color: #6a7685;">If Qualified → proceed to Step 3</span></li>
            <li><span style="color: #6a7685;">If Caution → review jointly with technical docs</span></li>
            <li><span style="color: #6a7685;">If Disqualify → do not pitch, update Portal to "Closed — Not Qualified"</span></li>
          </ol>

          <!-- Alert box -->
          <div style="max-width: 460px; margin: 0 auto; background: #fdeeee; color: #b42318; border: 1px solid #f5c7c7; border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px 18px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;">
            <strong>Ø If not eligible:</strong>
            Qualify out. Don’t pitch an unqualified opportunity.
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Gate -->
        <div style="border-top: 1px solid #d9e1e8; background: #f8fafb; padding: 28px 20px; display: flex; justify-content: center;">
          <div style="background: #edf5db; border: 1px solid #cfe09e; border-radius: 14px; padding: 22px 24px; text-align: center; max-width: 360px; width: 100%;">
            <div style="width: 28px; height: 28px; margin: 0 auto 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: #7ac70c; color: #ffffff; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700;">
              2
            </div>
            <div style="font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: #4c6b17; margin-bottom: 10px;">
              GATE
            </div>
            <h3 style="margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.35; color: #476b0f; font-weight: 700;">
              Customer Eligibility Confirmed
            </h3>
            <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; color: #6f7d4d;">
              <strong>Output:</strong> Qualification Tool completed with a "Qualified" result
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
